    <<jump TeacherApology>>
===

title: TeacherApology
---
<<lighten>>
{$teacherName}: I'm so sorry, Mira. It's just that you're the only florist in town, and I didn't want to go and do nothing again like last year, and-
<<darken>>
{$floristName}: It's alright. Please, don't apologize. I appreciate the gesture.
<<jump IfItsAlright>>
===

title: IfItsAlright
---
<<darken>>
{$floristName}: If it's alright, I'll do Pranas' wth my own inclusions.
<<jump TeacherOfferPayment>>
===

title: TeacherOfferPayment
---
<<lighten>>
{$teacherName}: Of course, I'm sorry. Please, let me pay more for it all.
<<darken>>
{$floristName}: Absolutely not. This is something I need. Besides, {$closeFriendName}'s already paid for an order, so I'll be okay.
<<jump TeacherEnding>>
===

title: TeacherEnding
---
<<lighten>>
{$teacherName}: ... Alright. But please, let me know if you'd like payment. I'm more than happy to.
<<darken>>
{$floristName}: I will. Now please, I need to get working.
<<jump TeacherLeaves>>
===

